original_font_information.trademark: Amiko is a trademark of Impallari Type.
original_font_information.designer: Pablo Impallari, Rodrigo Fuenzalida, Andres Torresi
original_font_information.description: Amiko is a clean and utilitarian font family specifically designed for maximum legibility at the smallest possible sizes ranges. They are intended for body text on the web and low resolution screens. Amiko supports Latin and Devanagari scripts.
